      "id": "step-2-entry-point",
      "title": "CLI Entry Point",
      "description": "The binary is built from a tiny entry point that immediately delegates into the CLI package. The CLI parses the user-facing subcommands — adding a repo, starting the daemon, checking status, and removing a repo — and wires them up to the rest of the system.",
