      "title": "End-to-End Tests & Benchmarks",
      "description": "The root-level end-to-end tests exercise the full daemon against real FUSE mounts, with platform-specific setup for macOS and Linux kept in separate files so each platform's quirks stay isolated. Two benchmark suites capture performance baselines — essential reading before tuning hydration or the filesystem layer.",
