      "title": "Supporting Packages",
      "description": "The smaller packages round out the system. Shared data structures live in a dedicated model package. A watcher reacts to overlay changes. An auth helper scrubs credentials out of log lines before they are emitted. And a logging package provides the structured JSON logger used across the daemon.",
